.#? ::num ::matrix.rotate_cols\n  shift columns of a matrix right N times
.#? ::num ::matrix.rotate_rows\n  shift rows of a matrix down N times
.{ Example:
    aya> [3 3]matrixR
    [[ 1 2 3 ]
     [ 4 5 6 ]
     [ 7 8 9 ]]

    aya> 1 [3 3]matrixR.rotate_rows
    [[ 7 8 9 ]
     [ 1 2 3 ]
